+import patchbukkit.itemstack.ItemMetadata;
+
+/**
+ * Explicit, cloneable Bukkit metadata adapter for Pumpkin's supported item
+ * component subset.
+ *
+ * <p>Unsupported getters return the Bukkit empty/default state. Unsupported
+ * mutations fail loudly so plugins never appear to save data that Pumpkin
